profile: With locations in Whitby, Oshawa, Ontario, Canada, Avoca Pools serves the entire Regional Municipality Of Durham (Durham Region) and provides full service installation, support services and pricing costs for custom inground swimming pools, safety covers, swimming pool renovations, weekly pool maintenance, seasonal pool opening, pool closing and more. With 25 years of industry experience and nearly 600 pools installed, we pride ourselves on customer service and focus on the smallest of details. We also specialize in delivering projects on-time and always within the specified budget. Call (905) 242-3008 or visit us online for more information and a project quote.
